<dl id="n12127e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12127e">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12127e"> 127(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> lay buried in Dominican / graveyard</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Des la&iuml;cs se faisaient enterrer au cimeti&egrave;re des religieux. C&apos;&eacute;tait pour les finances des paroisses une perte s&egrave;che. <br><font color="green">[Laymen were burried at the cemetery of the monks. That represented a clear loss for the finances of the parishes.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 26</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
